### Thank you for your hard work ###
This tool is just the best! I've been struggling to receive my earnings as a Walmart Spark Driver. Upon performing a Google search I discovered of other drivers reporting similar issues. I decided to write an open source app to support gig workers. Your app assisted me in creating a Privacy Policy in no time.

This is "theeee" Policy Generator app to utilize for anybody that needs policy documents. I began my tech career in 1998 and I recognize quality software when I use it. I'll be recommending this to my clients and am available to contribute to this project if needed. Thank you for developing a fantastic tool!
